devdoc.details: Only to be deployed on the home of the ZOR token

params._wantAmt: amount of Want token to deposit/stake

params._maxMarketMovementAllowed: The max slippage allowed. (included here just to implement interface; otherwise unused)

returns._0: uint256 Amount of Want token obtained

params._amount: The Want token quantity to exchange
params._maxMarketMovementAllowed: The max slippage allowed for swaps. (included here just to implement interface; otherwise unused)

params._amount: The amount of the tokens to transfer
params._to: The address to transfer tokens to
params._token: Address of the ERC20 token to transfer

initialize(address,(uint256,(address,add.details: NOTE: Only to be deployed on home chain!

params._initValue: A VaultZorroInit struct that contains all constructor args
params._timelockOwner: The designated timelock controller address to act as owner

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._entranceFeeFactor: Entrance fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)
params._withdrawFeeFactor: Withdrawal fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._wantAmt: The amount of Want token to withdraw

returns._0: uint256 the number of shares removed
